Changelog
=========

v0.1.6
======

- New: XmlOptions.ElementName property. Holds the XML element name used when the object is serialized. If null (the default) the class name will be used instead.

v0.1.5
======

Released on 20.5.2016

- New: DelegateValidator constructor overload with no PropertyName argument.

v0.1.4
======

Released on 5.8.2015

- Fix: ReadXML, cannot convert to Nullable on int? fields. Closes #3.

v0.1.3
======

Released on 31.7.2015

- New: ListOfStringLengthValidator.
- Fix: Deserialize List<int>. Closes FatturaElettronicaPA/FatturaElettronicaPA#9.
- Fix: Deserialize List<string>. Closes FatturaElettronicaPA/FatturaElettronicaPA#8.
- Fix: Don't hang on empty XML nodes. Closes FatturaElettronicaPA/FatturaElettronicaPA#7.
- Fix: Align AssemblyFileVersion to AssemblyVersion. Closes #2.

v0.1.2
======

Released on 14.7.2015

- Fix: Also validate properties which are of List<BusinessObjectBase> type.
  Closes #1.

v0.1.1
======

Released on 7.4.2015

- Fix: ReadXML raises an exception converting Decimal? type. Closes
  FatturaElettronicaPA/FatturaElettronicaPA#3.


v0.1
====

Released on 9.2.2015

- Initial release.
